# Citron Bloom + Inkblot integration

## Modes

- **Dev default**: Citron Bloom (`import.meta.env.DEV` without `?fluid`).
- **`?fluid`**: Raymarched fluid flower + **orbit** camera (`AnimationSystem` `orbit` mode).
- **Production**: Bloom only with `?citronBloom` (`=medium` | `low` for LOD).

`parseCitronBloomMode()` lives in [`src/inkblotApp.ts`](src/inkblotApp.ts).

## Engine layout (`engines/citron-bloom/`)

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| `bloom-core` | `palette.ts`, `tokens.ts`, LOD `types.ts`, instanced leaves |
| `bloom-curves` | DNA / stem tubes + shaders |
| `bloom-flora` | `ProceduralFlower`, `FloralAssembly`, `BloomPhaseController` |
| `bloom-particles` | GPGPU points |
| `bloom-postprocess` | `CitronBloomComposer` (bloom, glow, grade, `FilmPass`) |
| `bloom-ui` | React HUD (optional) |

Path alias: `@citron-bloom-engine` → `engines/citron-bloom`.

## Scroll → bloom

- [`ScrollSystem`](src/systems/scrollSystem.ts) damps `progress` [0,1]; virtual scroll height in [`index.html`](index.html) (`#virtual-scroll-space`).
- Tick order in [`inkblotApp.ts`](src/inkblotApp.ts): `scrollSystem` → `interactionSystem` → `setScrollProgress` + `animationSystem` → `audioSystem`, then `citronBloomComponent.setBloomFromScroll`, then components.
- Easing: [`CitronBloomComponent.setBloomFromScroll`](src/components/citronBloomComponent.ts); phase smoothing: [`createCitronBloomScene`](engines/citron-bloom/examples/createCitronBloomScene.ts) `BloomPhaseController` `smoothSpeed`.

## Camera

- [`AnimationSystem`](src/systems/animationSystem.ts): `CameraMotionMode` **`orbit`** (fluid) vs **`delicate`** (bloom: fixed framing, micro drift, pointer parallax).
- [`InkblotCamera.setDampFactor`](src/core/camera.ts) is lowered (~2.25) in bloom mode.
- [`InkblotControls`](src/core/controls.ts): `OrbitControls` **disabled** by default.

## 3D UI text

- [`Sections3DComponent`](src/components/sections3D.ts): Troika `Text` on a ring; **Y-axis billboard** each frame (`atan2` toward camera) so copy stays screen-parallel.

## Palette

- App: [`src/utils/colors.ts`](src/utils/colors.ts) `PALETTE` / `COLORS`.
- Engine meshes: [`engines/citron-bloom/bloom-core/palette.ts`](engines/citron-bloom/bloom-core/palette.ts) + [`tokens.ts`](engines/citron-bloom/bloom-core/tokens.ts) `BloomTokens`.

## Tuning

- **LOD**: `BLOOM_LOD_PROFILES` in [`bloom-core/types.ts`](engines/citron-bloom/bloom-core/types.ts).
- **Post (bloom mode)**: `CitronBloomComposer` constructor options in [`inkblotApp.ts`](src/inkblotApp.ts) + defaults in [`citronBloomComposer.ts`](engines/citron-bloom/bloom-postprocess/citronBloomComposer.ts).

When changing bloom timing, coordinate **scroll mapping**, **phase `smoothSpeed`**, and **virtual scroll height** together.

